@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (0.57 * wp.cos(tmp))
    v2 = ((tmp + (v2 + 0.17 / v0 + 0.78)) + wp.sin(wp.abs(v1 + 0.80)))
    v0 = wp.sin(0.97)
    v2 = wp.exp(wp.sin(v1))
    tmp = v0
    tmp = wp.abs(0.59)
    data[tid] = v0
